N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6210.3 - Submission of procedures for unofficial tally of results of election

State Regulations

County boards which adopt procedures pursuant to Election Law
section 9-126(3) shall file such procedures with the State Board of
